snippet.textDisplay:
Yeah, still no doubt intel will come back on top after a while.

Amd was on top in the late 00's, then intel surpassed them for most of the 10's, and now amd is back on top in the early 20's, by the late 20's though I have no doubt intel will be back on top.

Also, as much you guys like to think the success of a company is mostly nature, it's got a lot more nurture and environmental factors than you'd like to think. If intel actually does fall and amd becomes absolute king for a decade or more, then they'll end up exactly like intel, no doubt about it. They already said now that they're ahead they can feel warranted pricing them more, if they end up on top for too long they'll just be doing small changes at inflated prices just like intel.
